div.p:
God by his Prophet Ieremie (ſaith, Goe to the iſles of Chittim, and behold; 
                  Ier. 2. 10. 
                  and ſend vnto Kedar, and take diligent heede, and ſee whether there be ſuch things. Our moſt gratious God, compares his people of the Jewes, with the Paganes: And will he not much more compare vs chriſtians with them? And is it not a ſhame for vs to be ouercome of them in charitie towards our brethren? Surely, if we be, in the day of iudgement they ſhall condemne vs.
